      "repair_reason": "- [P1] No ClawSweeper repair job is appropriate: the code change appears narrow, but merge should wait on maintainer proof policy and scope judgment for the broader linked issue.; Cleared: The diff is limited to in-memory gateway/agent timeout handling and tests; it does not touch dependencies, workflows, secrets, package metadata, or external code execution. (sha=f0be7cfc416ea0fccbd8721603e0b63e3ea6d1aa)",
      "review_summary": "The PR exports the hard-timeout phase predicate, updates `waitForAgentJob` to forward pending hard-timeout snapshots from the fallback timer, and adds hard/soft timeout regression coverage.\n\nPR surface: Source +13, Tests +155. Total +168 across 4 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-reproducible: current main records pending timeout snapshots but the outer `waitForAgentJob` timer currently returns only pending errors or null. I did not run a fresh live parent/subagent timeout in this read-only review.",
